    "description": {
      "short": "A sleek medium-sized exploration vessel built for long-range scientific missions",
      "full": "The SSV Wanderer is a state-of-the-art exploration vessel designed for extended deep space missions. Equipped with advanced sensors, laboratories, and defensive systems, she's capable of surviving months in uncharted space while conducting comprehensive scientific research.",
      "appearance": "Streamlined hull with distinctive blue and silver plating. Two large sensor arrays extend from the dorsal section. The ship features rotating habitat sections for artificial gravity."
    }
  },
